posting_body: ['No Brokers Fee* Renovated STUDIO w/ Separate Kitchen *Kew Gardens Near LIRR', 'Listing ID #: 464001', 'Address: 118-80 Metropolitan AVENUE, #1EE', 'Price: $1,875', 'Property Type: Apartment', 'Bedrooms: 0.5 (STUDIO)', 'Bathrooms: 1.0', 'Floor: 1', 'Pets: Pets OK', 'Building Amenities', 'Elevator', 'Laundry', 'Apartment Amenities', 'Dining Room', 'Dishwasher', 'Granite Kitchen', 'Hardwood', 'High Ceilings', 'Marble Bath', 'Renovated', 'Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Welcome home to this gorgeous large STUDIO Apartment in Kew Gardens.', 'This Studio has a separate kitchen with beautiful cabinets, granite countertop and stainless steel appliances including a dishwasher.', 'Hardwood floors throughout apartment.', 'Come see this spacious apartment before its gone !', 'Conveniently located on Metropolitan Avenue and Lefferts Blvd, near the Q10 Bus just minutes away from the E and F Train and a couple of blocks from the LIRR.', 'Or even JFK airport.', '*Live in Super *Heat and Hot Water Included *Pets okay case by case', 'CHARM OF THE PRE-WAR ERA ABOUNDS IN THIS SOPHISTICATED BUILDING!', 'LOCATED IN THE HEART OF KEW GARDENS,BEAUTIFUL NEIGHBORHOOD.', "YOU'LL ENJOY PROXIMITY TO ALL SHOPS, RESTAURANTS FOR YOUR CONVENIENCE AND NY'S BEAUTIFUL FOREST PARK.", 'PUBLIC TRANSPORTATION', 'JUST RIGHT AROUND THE CORNER OF THE BUILDING.', 'David Kusayev', 'Phone: 718-864-4543', 'Mobile: 718-864-4543', 'Fax: 718-456-7188', 'Email: <URL>', 'Hillel Realty Group \xa0 718-864-4543 \xa0 718-864-4543 \xa0 FAX 718-456-7188 \xa0 <URL>', 'POSTED BY REALTYMX™', 'To view, call or text David Kusayev at 718-864-4543']
